    "%@ %@, %@ (%@)" : {
      "comment" : "A label describing a soccer goal with the minute, scorer, and goal type. The first argument is the minute the goal was scored. The second argument is the name of the player who scored. The third argument is the name of the goal type. The fourth argument is the short tag for the goal type.",
